    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-808d-bb11-ce83d61df066",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Early identification of students who may underperform is relevant and, for that reason, authors propose an algorithm that predicts final grade of a student in course. The algorithm is able to identify optimal prediction and optimal moment of prediction.",
