    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80d0-9b0f-de924d2ebb8d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors test their model on a sample of 700 undergraduate students taking an introductory digital signal processing course. Authors argue that model is effective method of early identification.",
